"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"In the 1980s, a group of science fiction writers were contemplating a New Vision: A near future world not far from us, not so near, in which the Earth is highly integrated under the control of information networks, the development of science and technology makes people and machines hard to separate you and me. The high-rise buildings in the city are surrounded by dense neon blocks..\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/yNZd8vopXtOhwrooajH_h.gif?height=200&width=500)\\n\\nThis new wave of literature from science fiction\\n\\nEventually evolved into a powerful subculture\\n\\n**C Y B E R P U N K**\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/QF8INSpMmJKWQem5wMWjc.gif?height=281&width=500)\\n\\nYou may not know what cyberpunk is, but you’ve certainly seen the appeal of cyberpunk in screen classics like Blade Runner, the Matrix, Ghost in the Shell and Akira.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/Agxc7Us62x-EJwlZ6VENY.gif?height=225&width=540)\\n\\nIt is chaotic, unconventional, yet in this seemingly discordant state of control of the appropriate rhythm, a school of its own.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/TmPf0LkyMbhcBGizcxBlL.gif?height=223&width=500)\\n\\nNow, as what was once a near-future world is becoming more and more concrete, what seems like a fantasy prophecy is beginning to come true. In the twenty-one St Century, we still need this punk spirit to break through the boundaries of space and time, to explore the new core of cyberspace in this vision of impending Armageddon, to find a way to rebuild freedom and hope.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/YGqQ4-R24sviVCtoxjjG3.gif?height=487&width=499)\\n\\n                                                              CYBERCITY\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/odf4hLJRM7VhBkIyxw9nH.jpeg?height=1080&width=1080)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/YgLnmbQ-DBPZY_Fs-2OdY.jpeg?height=1621&width=1080)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/ecO6VYaoLvcVLT4gQ486J.jpeg?height=698&width=658)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/QbjD91PHkZVGCXk8l0f8a.jpeg?height=607&width=1080)\\n\\n### \\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/FTi8TjQmo0pz0zXxQmyLZ.gif?height=359&width=635)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/_GP4jBhoGowdRrtLoyz4T.gif?height=640&width=640)\\n\\n**HIGH TECH， LOW LIFE**\\n\\n**SEE YOU IN CYBER FUTURE！**\",\"timestamp\":1634451085,\"title\":\"C Y B E R P U N K\"},\"digest\":\"XkCQmaoMD03RiWtIpH34sKnQpRbbPO100sbjN4AjqQE\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x528F2AbCD700ba6CD101050a12c87D3CD0dBC4bf\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"gnMYasgyt7g_iANsr-IDcq745f0oXGgnDBt-Hgpu6kg\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"RVHxQTIu0Nct4daTynL4coZhzk3ehgAohlDQVdu_gYc\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"lEdHCEaY5e54beRgZucgcsOF2XCfraXcOElysbpx62Nvm2ZmekYBKQVFPVW8y9Rv9QdLIakzWeh9AdCpj4t3eQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x4313c222b243ceb6f0c4ea633c3dc498de234e1421ee97562461224f115c4f976ef805b8415c33d7b167e7197eab958db8333b68b08525c2993e3f38fc9a06971c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"gnMYasgyt7g_iANsr-IDcq745f0oXGgnDBt-Hgpu6kg\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"RVHxQTIu0Nct4daTynL4coZhzk3ehgAohlDQVdu_gYc\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"XkCQmaoMD03RiWtIpH34sKnQpRbbPO100sbjN4AjqQE\"}"